      "message": "[Medium] Line 86: The comment says connectivityChanged(true) is only needed for calls, but the code runs it for every high-priority background push. The new classifier explicitly notes that regular DHT values can also be high priority, so message/sync pushes may still force a full DHT/SIP reconnect and undermine the battery-saving goal. Suggested fix:\n```suggestion\nif (isCallPush \u0026\u0026 remoteMessage.originalPriority \u003d\u003d RemoteMessage.PRIORITY_HIGH) {\n    app?.hardwareService?.connectivityChanged(true)\n}\n```",
